    <item>
      <title>谷歌将重点关注下一版本 Android 软件的安全性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/google-focuses-on-security-with-next-version-of-android-software</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc.旗下的谷歌正在增强最新版本Android的安全功能，Android是世界上最受欢迎的移动操作系统，并在该公司的年度开发者大会上预览了该系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/google-focuses-on-security-with-next-version-of-android-software</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛科技大师称人工智能刺激“文科的复仇”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/goldman-tech-guru-says-ai-spurring-revenge-of-the-liberal-arts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在这家华尔街巨头帮助运营技术业务和创新的乔治·李 (George Lee) 表示，人工智能将对高盛集团乃至整个金融行业产生深远影响，但需要人类的帮助来控制风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/goldman-tech-guru-says-ai-spurring-revenge-of-the-liberal-arts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:56:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着风向的转变，对油砂城的野火威胁有所缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/wildfire-threat-to-oil-sands-capital-seen-easing-as-winds-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着气温下降和风向转变，野火对加拿大油砂工业非官方首都的威胁预计会减轻，但降雨完全浇灭大火的可能性仍然很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/wildfire-threat-to-oil-sands-capital-seen-easing-as-winds-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
